ved. A column was added (using the ArcGIS Pro \u201cadd field\u201d tool) to be able to classify actions according to barometer categories. REDD + Secretariat: The land use rasters for 2015-2019 were considered. The \u201ccombine\u201d raster analysis tool was used to determine the types of actions that correspond to a change from non-forest use (agriculture, pasture) to forest use. Added (add field) a column to classify the actions according to the categories of the Barometer. SINAC: Tabulated information was received in", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "68f3282c-5a77-460c-a1cb-d3d302b3dafd": {"__data__": {"id_": "68f3282c-5a77-460c-a1cb-d3d302b3dafd", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/resources/grey-literature/application-restoration-barometer-costa-rica", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Application of the Restoration Barometer in Costa Rica", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/resources/grey-literature/application-restoration-barometer-costa-rica", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "951f335188596dc62cd42dbecbf5cda397a54418ea2c1038e021a665c1c68841"}, "3": {"node_id": "f13a6599-46a8-4f61-a6b1-f6c9b6df0b51", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/resources/grey-literature/application-restoration-barometer-costa-rica", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "73282887a34fd8a083cd13262fb3650f632e9